When you may collect your personal data and other information through an application or service, as described below:
Personal data that you provide through the App: When you voluntarily provide such information, we may collect your personal data, such as your name, age, address, etc.
By voluntarily providing us with personal data, you consent to our use of this data in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
Unrecognizable or aggregated data: When you pass an application or service, we receive and store certain personally unrecognizable information. This information is collected passively using a variety of techniques and cannot be used to specifically identify you. We may also disclose aggregated user statistics to describe our services to current and potential business partners and other third parties for other legitimate purposes.
2.How to use information
We use your personal information to serve you.
Generate and view reports and data about our user base and service usage patterns.
Analyze the accuracy, effectiveness, usability or popularity of the service,
Improve the content and functionality of the service
Allow us to personalize what you see on the service.
Please note that if you choose not to provide us with certain personal information, we may not be able to provide you with services.
